xA">Nguyễn Bỉnh Khiêm</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Kh%E1%BB%91c-L%C3%BD-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-th%C6%B0-Chi-Ph%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/poem-6qTAtGo_ZyzKWNRjYhRq7g">Khốc Lý thượng thư Chi Phương - 哭李尚書之芳</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Ki%C3%AAm-h%C3%A0/poem-fgWEdyuWUL6csRCd-sNhIA">Kiêm hà - 蒹葭</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-Ph%E1%BA%A1m-H%C3%A0m/K%E1%BB%B3-13/poem-Bc-ljWZAQhUljNPLOKTfcQ">Kỳ 13 - 其十三</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-Ph%E1%BA%A1m-H%C3%A0m/author-FUm0aTv6MMEhKSvKSGMoVA">Vũ Phạm Hàm</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Ti%E1%BB%83u-h%C3%A0n-th%E1%BB%B1c-chu-trung-t%C3%A1c/poem-2mMZILOCuzgaEX--NzW2vg">Tiểu hàn thực chu trung tác - 小寒食舟中作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tri%E1%BB%87u-H%E1%BB%97/Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-An-thu-v%E1%BB%8Dng/poem-wtLuaeK-CSCze4WDaoAXxg">Trường An thu vọng - 長安秋望</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tri%E1%BB%87u-H%E1%BB%97/author-ZK21rLayK3mmuHkvR5sQcg">Triệu Hỗ</a>)<br></div>	</div>
